title: Dunbeholden F.C.
text: Dunbeholden F.C. are a <a href="Jamaica">Jamaica</a>n <a href="association%20football">football</a> club competing in the <a href="National%20Premier%20League">National Premier League</a>, gaining promotion for the <a href="2018%E2%80%9319%20National%20Premier%20League">2018–19 season</a>.
